**** Packaging Python Application Template ****

Reference: https://uoftcoders.github.io/studyGroup/lessons/python/packages/lesson/
            https://setuptools.readthedocs.io/en/latest/setuptools.html#declaring-dependencies


Build intallation file command:
    python setup.py bdist_wininst


Befor building the installation file, put all application source codes into 'src\gis_td' folder.
After installed, the applications will be in 'C:\Python27\Lib\site-packages\gis_td'.